{"id":1150529761,"question_id":69,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"4 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1705652399,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"1 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1150529761/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Sqrt(x)","memory":"40.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int mySqrt(int x) {\n        \n        if(x<2) return x;\n        long st= 1, ed=x/2;\n        \n        while(st<ed){\n            \n            long mid = ed-(ed-st)/2;\n            long p = myPow(mid, 2);\n            if(p==x){\n                return (int)mid;\n            }else if(p>x){\n                ed = mid-1;\n            }else{\n                st = mid;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return (int)st;\n    }\n    \n    \n    private long myPow(long x, int n){\n        \n        if(n==0) return 1;\n        \n        if(n<0){\n            n=-n;\n            x=1/x;\n        }\n        \n        if(n%2==0){\n            return myPow(x*x, n/2);\n        }else \n            return x*myPow(x*x, n/2);\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"sqrtx","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
